Author: sparklypinktutu
Text: I did the same! It’s my face that really startled me. Not only was I critically underweight, but my nutrition was jacked up. Like no iron, no protein, no calcium. Nothing. I was bug-eyed, and my eyes looked constantly watery. My hair was so thin and my hairline was gone. I had wrinkles. Mind you, this was when I was 14-15 years old.   When I was experiencing this at the time, I didn’t see how... dead I looked. My under eye bags were totally sunken in and a sickly bruise brown. It was just, sad.

Author: lauryleah
Text: thank you for sharing this. i appreciate the honesty sm
